snippet.title: TowerFall Trailer
snippet.description:
1-4 player archery combat. Enter the land of TowerFall with your friends and engage in the noble and brutal tradition of bow-and-arrow combat.

Learn more at www.towerfall-game.com
Follow development at towerfall.tumblr.com

Trailer by Kert Gartner
Game by Matt Thorson
Graphics by Miniboss (Pedro Medeiros and Amora Bettany)
Music by Alec Holowka
Sounds by Power Up Audio (Kevin Regamey and Jeff Tangsoc)

www.mattmakesgames.com
